    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Elenchus' Dev Docs"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"eaea4c94-7d0c-517b-afd0-1aec4bf607ae","excerpt":"환경    Node.js 프로젝트 초기 설정  파일 생성됨. Typescript 및 ESLint 패키지 설치 코딩컨벤션은 eslint-config-naver를 사용함. Typescript 초기 설정  파일 생성됨. ESLint Config…","html":"<h2>환경</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm 8.1.2</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">tsc Version 4.6.3</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">eslint v8.13.0</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Node.js 프로젝트 초기 설정</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> init</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code> 파일 생성됨.</p>\n<h2>Typescript 및 ESLint 패키지 설치</h2>\n<p>코딩컨벤션은 <a href=\"https://github.com/naver/eslint-config-naver\">eslint-config-naver</a>를 사용함.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i -D typescript\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i -D eslint eslint-config-naver eslint-plugin-import\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i -D @typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin @typescript-eslint/parser</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Typescript 초기 설정</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npx tsc -init</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">tsconfig.json</code> 파일 생성됨.</p>\n<h2>ESLint Config 생성</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">.eslintrc</code> 파일을 생성하여 아래 내용 작성.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// .eslintrc</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"parser\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@typescript-eslint/parser\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"plugins\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"@typescript-eslint\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"extends\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Naver Javascript Coding Conventions 적용</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"naver\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 만약 ES5인 경우 \"naver/es5\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// TypeScript ESLint recommanded style 적용</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"plugin:@typescript-eslint/eslint-recommended\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Linting Script 추가</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code>의 <code class=\"language-text\">scripts</code> 부분에 아래와 같이 Linting script 추가</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// package.json</span>\n<span class=\"token string-property property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"lint\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"eslint src/**/*.ts\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"lint:fix\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"eslint --fix src/**/*.ts\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Typescript에 ESLint 적용하기","date":"2022년 04월 19일","description":"Typescript로 개발할 때 정적 코드 분석 도구 ESLint를 적용하여 코딩 컨벤션을 통일하자.","tags":["Typescript","ESLint"]}},"previous":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"eaea4c94-7d0c-517b-afd0-1aec4bf607ae","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":null}},
